---
title: Call For Proposals for Poster Presentations
description: Poster Presentations at PyCon India 2025
layout: base.njk
---

{% from "components/button.njk" import button %}

<div class="w-full h-auto bg-pycon-blue -mb-24 px-[6%] flex flex-col md:flex-row">
    <div class="pt-32 pb-8 md:pb-32 w-full lg:w-[70%]">
        <div class="black-han-sans-regular font-normal text-3xl md:text-5xl md:text-center text-[#FFFFFF] text-center lg:text-left">
            Poster Presentations
        </div>
        <div class="text-md lg:text-xl pt-12 text-[#FFFFFF] lg:pr-10 text-justify">
            <p>PyCon India 2025 invites proposals for poster presentations that encourage creative and interactive sharing of projects and ideas within the Python community. Featuring a graphical summary on an A0-sized board, this format allows presenters to engage with attendees in an informal setting, making it ideal for showcasing early-stage concepts, niche topics, and research while fostering meaningful discussions and networking opportunities.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="lg:w-[30%] w-[80%] lg:mt-60 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto">
        <img src="{{ env.baseUrl }}img/assets/laptop.svg" alt="Guide" class="w-[40%] lg:w-[60%] transition-transform duration-100" style="animation: floating 2s ease-in-out infinite;">
        <img src="{{ env.baseUrl }}img/assets/filter-coffee.svg" alt="Guide" class="w-[40%] lg:w-[60%] transition-transform duration-100" style="animation: floating 2s ease-in-out infinite;">
    </div>
</div>

<div class="absolute top-2/5 right-4 md:block">
    <img src="{{ env.baseUrl }}img/assets/star-lime-vector.svg" alt="Groovy star" class="md:w-16 md:h-16 w-10 h-10">
</div>

<div class="absolute md:top-3/4 pt-52 md:right-20 right-12 md:block">
    <img src="{{ env.baseUrl }}img/assets/star-pink-vector.svg" alt="Groovy star" class="md:w-16 md:h-16 w-10 h-10">
</div>

<div class="main-container pt-16 md:pt-48 bg-lavender w-full h-auto px-[6%]">
    <div class="pb-40 md:pb-60 lg:pb-[20%] w-full text-justify lg:w-[70%]">
        <div class="mt-24 md:-mt-32 lg:-mt-20 text-md lg:text-xl font-light">
            <div class="black-han-sans-regular font-normal text-3xl md:text-5xl md:text-center text-[#000000] text-center lg:text-left">
                <p>Important Dates</p>
            </div>
            <div class="pt-12 text-[#000000] lg:pr-10">
                <ul class="list-none space-y-4">
                    <li class="flex">
                        <img src="{{ env.baseUrl }}img/assets/circle-lime.svg" alt="Bullet Icon" class="w-4 h-4 mr-2 mt-1">
                        <span><span class="font-semibold">Submission Open:</span> 11 July 2025</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex">
                        <img src="{{ env.baseUrl }}img/assets/circle-lime.svg" alt="Bullet Icon" class="w-4 h-4 mr-2 mt-1">
                        <span><span class="font-semibold">Submission Deadline:</span> <del>10 August 2025</del> 17 August 2025 (extended)</span>

                    </li>
                    <li class="flex">
                        <img src="{{ env.baseUrl }}img/assets/circle-lime.svg" alt="Bullet Icon" class="w-4 h-4 mr-2 mt-1">
                        <span><span class="font-semibold">Speaker Notifications:</span> 20 August 2025</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex">
                        <img src="{{ env.baseUrl }}img/assets/circle-lime.svg" alt="Bullet Icon" class="w-4 h-4 mr-2 mt-1">
                        <span><span class="font-semibold">Poster Presentations:</span> 13-14 September 2025 (afternoon session)</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="flex justify-center lg:justify-start pt-8">
                {{ button(text="Submit a Proposal", url="https://cfp.in.pycon.org/2025/cfp", lime_bg=true, env = env, disabled=true) }}
            </div>
            <div class="text-center lg:text-left mt-4 text-red-600 font-semibold">
              <p>Proposals are closed. Thank you for your submissions!</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="pt-12 lg:pt-32 text-md lg:text-xl font-light">
            <div class="black-han-sans-regular font-normal text-3xl md:text-5xl md:text-center text-[#000000] text-center lg:text-left">
                <p>Submission Guidelines</p>
            </div>
            <div class="pt-12 text-[#000000] lg:pr-10">
                <ul class="list-none space-y-4">
                  <li class="flex">
                      <img src="{{ env.baseUrl }}img/assets/circle-lime.svg" alt="Bullet Icon" class="w-4 h-4 mr-2 mt-1">
                      <span>Maximum of 3 presenters per submission.</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex">
                      <img src="{{ env.baseUrl }}img/assets/circle-lime.svg" alt="Bullet Icon" class="w-4 h-4 mr-2 mt-1">
                      <span>Provide links for the attendees to know more about the topic and connect.</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex">
                      <img src="{{ env.baseUrl }}img/assets/circle-lime.svg" alt="Bullet Icon" class="w-4 h-4 mr-2 mt-1">
                      <span>An actual poster is <b>not</b> required during submission.</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex">
                      <img src="{{ env.baseUrl }}img/assets/circle-lime.svg" alt="Bullet Icon" class="w-4 h-4 mr-2 mt-1">
                      <span>No slides or formal talks allowed, only physical posters and discussions.</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex">
                      <img src="{{ env.baseUrl }}img/assets/circle-lime.svg" alt="Bullet Icon" class="w-4 h-4 mr-2 mt-1">
                      <span>All presenters should have knowledge about the poster topic.</span>
                  </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="pt-12 lg:pt-32 text-md lg:text-xl font-light">
            <div class="black-han-sans-regular font-normal text-3xl md:text-5xl md:text-center text-[#000000] text-center lg:text-left">
                <p>Selection Process</p>
            </div>
            <div class="pt-12 text-[#000000] lg:pr-10">
                <ul class="list-none space-y-4">
                  <li class="flex">
                      <img src="{{ env.baseUrl }}img/assets/circle-purple.svg" alt="Bullet Icon" class="w-4 h-4 mr-2 mt-1">
                      <span><span class="font-semibold">Shortlisting:</span> Proposals will be reviewed by the review committee for completeness and adherence to guidelines.</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex">
                      <img src="{{ env.baseUrl }}img/assets/circle-purple.svg" alt="Bullet Icon" class="w-4 h-4 mr-2 mt-1">
                      <span><span class="font-semibold">Review:</span> After getting shortlisted, you need to submit a PDF version of your poster for review.</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex">
                      <img src="{{ env.baseUrl }}img/assets/circle-purple.svg" alt="Bullet Icon" class="w-4 h-4 mr-2 mt-1">
                      <span><span class="font-semibold">Final Selection:</span> Shortlisted presenters will get notification and further steps.</span>
                  </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
